[Patient] Can you recommend exercises for me to do to help with my heart failure? 
[Healthcare Educator] Try indoor activities like yoga or dancing to stay safe in your neighborhood. 
[Patient] How can I afford indoor exercise options? 
[Healthcare Educator] Look for free online workout videos or community fitness classes to save money. 
[Patient] Will exercising really help my heart health? 
[Healthcare Educator] Yes, regular exercise can improve your cardiovascular health and energy levels. 
[Patient] What if I don't enjoy traditional exercises? 
[Healthcare Educator] Find activities you enjoy, like hiking or swimming, to make exercise fun and sustainable.